#bold[#magenta[Synopsis:]] steroids create #bold[directory] #cyan[--options]

  Creates a new Supersonic project in the target directory.

#bold[#magenta[Available options:]]

  #cyan[--language=<language>]
    Sets the script language used. Available languages:

    #bold[js]       JavaScript
    #bold[coffee]   CoffeeScript

  #cyan[--type=<type>]
    Sets the type of app created. Available types:
    
    #bold[mpa]      Creates a Multi-Page App (Supersonic default)
    #bold[spa]      Creates a Single-Page App
